{"tid":139873,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(復合)好馬不吃回頭草，好草不怕回頭吃！","createTime":"2017-03-01T18:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T05:49:11.000Z","uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58794d0368b2037c210feab9409e1082b1e94e81","tid":139873,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:09:21.000Z","msg":"話說同ex分左手，原因係知佢一直都放唔低之前鍾意既人，我就主動提出分手，但因為真係好中意佢，依家已經後悔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。由分手到依一刻都仲好想一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，做左好多野挽回都無結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n黎緊要考A-level（英國絲），所以想專注返係學業，但佢今日無啦啦同我個frd講話想同我做返朋友，唔想無左依段友誼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲打左一大段野比我，我睇得出佢只係想做朋友，唔係想挽回/發展。<br />\n所以想問各位，我應唔應該應佢機？因為我怕一應完，自己又再陷落去搞到無心機溫書，到時考衰左真係會好對唔住老豆老母比咁多錢我去外國讀書。<br />\n另外，我都擔心依家做返朋友係會frdzone左我，因為我打算考完個試會改變形象有個全新既自己，等佢有眼前一亮既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好感度上升！依家咁快做返朋友，效果好似會無咁好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就想問大家，如果我考完個試先再覆佢會唔會好啲？<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以分享下，ex心中有放唔低既人最後都選擇返自己而復合既成功例子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be98ce5b61cfbf598dad68c364337ff23154f7f","tid":139873,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人可以幫下我 真係好鍾意佢"},{"pid":"38339b185abbf8e44dc1a9de1b2b2d81dffd1844","tid":139873,"uid":53570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:12:43.000Z","msg":"Dont think too much, take a good sleep"},{"pid":"6a17dab9da4dff31a909b96a64515a778ed8e15b","tid":139873,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dont think too much, take a good sleep</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb3d2ec288f91646705d13f72452f725ee9d3d3","tid":139873,"uid":7463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"去馬啦，諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ed6ce8cdf89f270abe3fa406d9fa5cf5236013","tid":139873,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去馬啦，諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係點？依家應機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2fb585df40520fb0842ff43f2ae88f23b00306","tid":139873,"uid":4375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去馬啦，諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係點？依家應機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢暫時只係想做朋友，又放唔低個女仔，做返朋友有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6317d3439c51c4fca58bede092be85ff67e408c","tid":139873,"uid":5980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T19:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去馬啦，諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係點？依家應機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/